00:20:49.340 --> 00:20:51.900
And I really thought he'd
be a great match with David

00:20:51.900 --> 00:20:53.730
to help bring out the ideas.

00:20:53.730 --> 00:20:56.310
And I remember it was like
the first day in the studio,

00:20:56.310 --> 00:20:59.350
and it was like the first
line of the first song.

00:20:59.350 --> 00:21:01.330
We're like, OK, take one.

00:21:01.330 --> 00:21:04.040
And then it was like 100
versions of the line,

00:21:04.040 --> 00:21:05.890
and then Colin
came in the studio

00:21:05.890 --> 00:21:08.170
and David couldn't
hear us, so he

00:21:08.170 --> 00:21:10.677
was just seeing like me, Carrie,
and Colin, like-- you know?

00:21:10.677 --> 00:21:12.760
And then he was like, is
everything cool in there?

00:21:12.760 --> 00:21:13.520
We're like, yeah.

00:21:13.520 --> 00:21:14.450
We're just listening to an edit.

00:21:14.450 --> 00:21:14.950
Yeah.

00:21:14.950 --> 00:21:15.830
Everything's cool.

00:21:15.830 --> 00:21:18.500
