of four hours of trying

00:21:31.719 --> 00:21:33.737
to sing one song.

00:21:33.737 --> 00:21:34.320
BRAD: Exactly.

00:21:37.760 --> 00:21:40.350
So the first day
was a little rough,

00:21:40.350 --> 00:21:42.670
