the first day, I think,

00:21:48.730 --> 00:21:50.269
we got through not as much.

00:21:50.269 --> 00:21:51.310
DAVID DUCHOVNY: One song.

00:21:51.310 --> 00:21:51.600
One song.

00:21:51.600 --> 00:21:52.475
BRAD: Yeah, one song.

