and trying new things

00:22:51.070 --> 00:22:54.069
at this point in your career.

00:22:54.069 --> 00:22:54.860
DAVID DUCHOVNY: Oh.

00:22:58.710 --> 00:23:01.770
I think that when
I talk to my kids,

00:23:01.770 --> 00:23:04.170
I always talk to
them about failing.

00:23:04.170 --> 00:23:09.270
And And I was lying
in bed this morning,

00:23:09.270 --> 00:23:11.400
