it into "Bartlett's" today.

00:23:17.550 --> 00:23:21.440
So success is a lecturer.

00:23:21.440 --> 00:23:24.470
Failure is a teacher.

00:23:24.470 --> 00:23:25.628
Anybody?

00:23:25.628 --> 00:23:26.128
Not bad?

00:23:26.128 --> 00:23:27.260
[APPLAUSE]

00:23:27.260 --> 00:23:29.150
"Barlett's"?

00:23:29.150 --> 00:23:32.440
I don't like the word
lecturer, it's clunky.

00:23:32.440 --> 00:23:35.125
But anyway, that's
the way I feel.

00:23:35.125 --> 00:23:38.920
It's like, you don't
really learn from success.

00:23:38.920 --> 00:23:40.660
You learn maybe intellectually.

00:23:40.660 --> 00:23:45.710
