to be human being and an adult

00:23:45.710 --> 00:23:50.580
and a person and
empathetic and human.

00:23:50.580 --> 00:23:58.846
And so I always try to teach my
kids to be comfortable failing.

00:23:58.846 --> 00:24:00.470
Not comfortable,
that's the wrong word,

00:24:00.470 --> 00:24:02.420
but I think you
know what I mean.

00:24:02.420 --> 00:24:06.882
