just feel like, well, all

00:24:06.882 --> 00:24:09.340
I can do is fail and that's
like the worst that can happen.

00:24:09.340 --> 00:24:09.850
So what?

00:24:09.850 --> 00:24:12.570
So then I can try
something else,

00:24:12.570 --> 00:24:14.470
